s=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Can I use Framer Motion with Styled Components?","date":"02 Mar 2020"},"fields":{"slug":"/20200302-can-i-use-framer-motion-with-styled-components/","author":"mattperry","description":"Framer Motion is fully compatible with Styled Components. Take a look at how simple the two work together."}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/20200302-can-i-use-framer-motion-with-styled-components/","author":"mattperry","description":"Framer Motion is fully compatible with Styled Components. Take a look at how simple the two work together."}}